organic.title: National Domestic Violence Hotline: Domestic Violence Support
organic.snippet: Everyone deserves relationships free from domestic violence. When you're ready, we're here to listen with confidential support 24/7/365.

organic.title: ABOUT AWAIC
organic.snippet: Abused Women's Aid in Crisis (AWAIC) is the largest domestic violence safe shelter in Alaska. AWAIC provides services to women, men, and children.

organic.title: 24 Hour Crisis & Support Line - AWAIC
organic.snippet: We also have options for survivors who do not need emergency shelter but could use support, such as with filing a protective order, securing safe housing.
